name: Food Truck Empire
description: Food Truck Empire is an economic strategy/tycoon game where you manage your own fast-growing Food Truck enterprise. Compose your dishes, automatize their production, customize your trucks and research new tech - all to serve even the pickiest customers. The world of flavor is yours to conquer!

name: Alterborn
description: In this unique blend of multiple genres such as soulslike, roguelite, looter shooter and more, explore a one of a kind, grim and lawless world corrupted by a mysterious force.

name: The Time I Have Left
description: The Time I Have Left is a time-driven escape adventure with RPG elements set in a complex underground facility. A mysterious phenomenon known only as ‘The Miasma’ has marked Aline for certain death.

name: Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas VR
description: Experience the story of Carl "CJ" Johnson (in VR), a man who is framed by a couple of cops for homicide and is forced on a journey that takes him across the entire state of San Andreas, to save his family and to take control of the streets.

name: Her Choice
description: A thrilling and plot rich otome romance visual novel

name: Purpose: Versus
description: An upcoming action RPG which takes place simultaneous to the story of Purpose: VERSA; its counterpart story in the Purpose timeline.

name: Warspace.io
description: WarSpace.io is an NFT-based play to earn game developed on the WAX blockchain. Thanks to the tokenized economy, players themselves control the market and build trade relations. Everyone can choose their own path: develop stone mining, engage in logging, restore the food industry or go deep underground in search of gold. Resources are needed to build new buildings, as well as to participate in pvp-battles.

name: Fantasy All Stars
description: Fantasy All Stars is the first Chinese MOBA game to incorporate 10v10 matches using a wide roster of anime characters from famous series chosen and voted by the community themselves.

name: Contrablade: Stadium Rush
description: Let it rip & control your own Contrablade to knock out your opponent and reach the farthest to unlock new parts, abilities, and upgrades in this addictive, simple to enjoy but hard to master unique physics fighting action roguelite arcade game!

name: The Witcher IV
description: The Witcher IV is a single-player, open-world RPG from CD PROJEKT RED. At the start of a new saga, players take on the role of Ciri, a professional monster slayer, and embark on a journey through a brutal dark-fantasy world.

name: Magical Escape
description:
In this game, you need to solve the puzzle to escape.
The game isn't really hard but you have to think.
The game isn't fully completed more maps and puzzles will come!

name: Faul!
description:
Faul! is a card game played online.. Just create a lobby to play the Faul! game with your friends. You can invite your friends by sharing the link of the lobby with them. Each team can have a maximum of 5 people.

The red team always starts the game first. In order to reach the set target score, the narrator tries to explain the words before him to his teammates without using the forbidden words. While a team is telling, a person from the other team can check the banned words.

The first team to reach the target score wins the game. It is easier to reach the target score as the red team is always the first narrator. Therefore, for the Blue team to win the game, it is sufficient to get 2 points less than the target score. To explain this with an example, if the game ends with 20 points, it is enough for the blue team to collect 18 points.

name: The Jellyfish Girl's Absolute Abnormal Adventure
description: The regular daily life of Key, a young jellyfish girl

name: Exorzine
description: In this game you start in a dungeon cell. Exorzine will try to stop you from escaping.

name: The Thief in the Dark
description: The Thief In the dark is an action adventure game featuring a heroine. You have to explore the underworld to defeat the unsealed devil and find equipment to defeat many monsters.

name: Valley Dash
description: Dash! Dash! Dash as far as you can in this NES inspired arcade take on action command RPG battle action! Pick a dasher, collect gear, build your party and gather upgrades to dash as far as you possibly can.

name: Banjo X
description: Banjo X was a remake of Banjo-Kazooie that Rareware were developing for the Xbox in 2005, which was eventually cancelled and redeveloped into Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts & Bolts.

name: Impossible Slasher! Hack and Slash
description: Defeat as many enemies as you can and unlock different characters with different abilities in this arcade Hack and Slash.

name: Maid in Witch Life!: Yakata de Hajimaru H na Miryou Seikatsu
Rooted
description: In this solo and multiplayer survival game, explore an ancient overgrown world full of dangers. Salvage, build, craft, hunt,.. and try to survive alone or with your friends in an evolving and fascinating post-apocalyptic environment. Powered by Unreal Engine 5.

name: Gladiator
description:
After death, the evil are faced with judgement by the divine order of their world. They are given a chance at redemption: to compete in the gauntlet against their peers and slay a cursed enemy of the pantheon. The Gladiators who succeed in their quest are born anew into the world, those who fail are damned eternally.

Possess a Gladiator and take part in the gauntlet. Team up with your friends and engage colossal enemies in souls-like boss fights, join in epic PVP medieval combat, and devise strategic machinations in a desperate bid for absolution. Immerse yourself in the atmospheric and glorious gamble for exoneration. Victory results in vindication, defeat leads only to ruin.

name: Rain in the Abyss
description: A SurvivalHorrror/Metroidvania game were the world has a constant rain, full of beauty, magic, horror and sadness. Discover an unique story that will touch each of your emotions.

name: Tynk! and the Final Phonorecord
description: Tynk! and the Final Phonorecord is a story about creating art, making friends, and exploring the weird grey area that exists between art and commodity. It's a goofy, thoughtful and sometimes moody little adventure starring an overzealous musician, Tynk Nimbus, on a quest to make her new album the next big thing. Solve puzzles, avoid bodily harm, and travel the coast on your quest to show your album to everyone who's anyone! Just remember to brace yourself-- safely navigating feedback is Tynk's biggest challenge yet.

name: Kirari Nangoku Komugiiro: Shiofuki Paradise he Youkoso!
Kimi to Boku to no Kishi no Hibi: Rakuen no Chevalier
Ero Zemi: Ecchi ni Yaru-ki ni ABC
Amayakashi na Kanojo: Boseiteki na Ayakashi Musume to Ama Ero Seikatsu Hajimemasu
description: You are a regular overworked company employee who's life is changed when he finds a beautiful girl sitting outside his home. She’s your niece, Anya, who tells you that her mother went on a trip overseas, and since her mother felt it would be too dangerous for her to live alone she was told to come stay with you. This is the start of your new life together. In exchange for letting her live with you, Anya offers to help around the house by cleaning, preparing meals, and giving you a lap to lay your head on when you get home from work. For you, she is like the perfect wife you always dreamed of. These feelings of love eventually change into another kind of love... and you can’t resist your heart's desires.

name: Girls Book Maker: Shiawase no Libretto
Case Clicker
description: CaseClicker is an incremental clicker game based around csgo and the jackpot/skin community. The goal is to open cases and get rich.

name: Seeds of Calamity
description: Take part in healing after the Great Calamity. Tend your farm, complete quests for the villagers, and explore dungeons filled with challenge and treasure in this cozy, solo-developed farming sim. Build a new life in a recovering world with your fluffy Spellbook Companion.

name: Arknights: Endfield
description: Arknights: Endfield is a real-time 3D RPG with strategic elements published by GRYPHLINE.

name: Hinekuremono no Gakuen Seishun Monogatari: Ore to Kanojo no Reversible
Kimi no Tonari de Koishiteru!: The Respective Happiness
Boku no Mirai ha, Koi to Kakin to.: Charge to the Future
Koi wa Sotto Saku Hana no you ni: Futari wa Eien ni Yorisotte Iku
Kizuna Kirameku Koi Iroha: Tsubaki Renka
Upgrade
description: Upgrade is an upcoming sci-fi, first-person shooter set in a dystopian, alternate reality in a research facility full of maniacal cyborgs.

name: Monaco 2
description:
Get your crew back together
The crack team of hackers and masterminds at Pocketwatch Games is in the backroom planning out Monaco II, the sequel to the hyper-stylized heist hit that PC Gamer called “one of the best co-op games of all time.”

The vision to pull off this job is simple. Bring in a new rogues’ gallery of skilled thieves and infiltration experts to play. Let them loose in an intriguing new setting. Test their skills in brain-bending 3D environments, procedurally generated by an AI mastermind designed to concoct high-stakes challenges and infinite sneaky, stealy fun.

And most of all, preserve the friend-fueled energy of the original: a mix of smarts, stealth, and frenzied improvisational mayhem when plans go awry. The big payday is the ultimate heist experience for you and your gang.

name: Whalefall
description: Whalefall takes place in a unique fantasy world with new places to discover, races to meet, and conflicts to resolve. Make friends and enemies, build your army, and maybe fall in love on the continent of Osfeld!

name: WEGO: WW2 Stalingrad
description: WEGO World War II: Stalingrad is the flagship of Brian Kelly's operational level, ground-centric, WEGOWW2 game system. Built on the framework of Desert War 1940-42, this hex-based wargame captures the drama of the epic German offensive to capture the industrial city of Stalingrad in the Summer of '42. It consists of a series of historical scenarios and campaigns that allow the players to explore the ebb and flow of the actual combat operations. It’s playable by both sides using hotseat, versus the AI, or Play By Email.

name: Trippers: Kanojo to no Gakuen Seikatsu o Hakai Suru, Ittsuu no Tegami
Koi wa Mofumofu! Love Me Teddy
Hara Katsu! 3: Kozukuri Business Haigyou no Kiki!?
Turtles!
description: In this action-puzzle game, you take control of Bonnie and all the other cute turtles and help as many of them as possible to get to the sea.

name: Chroma Chronicles
description: Fast, turn-based, PVP deckbuilding game created by streamer BoxBox. Recently launched on Kickstarter!

name: BR1
description: BR1: Infinite is the world's first risk-based shooter where players Pay-to-Spawn and Kill-to-Earn. Gamers are paid USD for every player they eliminate in game.

name: Footium
description: Footium is a Web3 Football Management game where players become the owner, manager and scout for their very own football club. Climb the divisions and compete in cups to win prizes by being a savvy spender, mastermind tactician and having a great eye for talent.

name: Circus Baby's Diner
description: Welcome to Circus Baby's Diner! It's a place to have loads of fun and enjoy pizza!

name: Power Rush
description:
In a universe where the earth is no longer enough for the human race, the USS has sent a team of miners, architects, engineers and scientists to create a sustainable planet for the human race.
The operation starts until one of the miners get in touch with a space crystal which gives him powers and alerts the inhabitants of the planet who later attack the space city.

name: Phenocore
description: Phenocore is a stylized First person shooter made by the team at Gumball Interactive.

name: Space Varments
description: Space Varments is a built-in game of the GP2X Wiz portable console.

name: Boomshine2x
description:
Boomshine2x is a game written in Fenix and available for the GP2x and the GP2x Wiz handhelds. It’s an authorised clone of the flash game Boomshine by Danny Miller.
It was one of the games released built-in on the GP2X Wiz portable console.

name: Tail-Tale
description: Tail-Tale is a built-in game of the GP2X Wiz portable console.

name: Myriad
description: Myriad is one of the built-in games of the GP2X Wiz portable console.

name: Wiztern
description: Wiztern is one of the games built-in on the GP2X Wiz portable console.

name: Sqdef
description:
Sqdef is a tower defense game for the GP2X handhelds. The goal is to prevent enemies from getting from one side of the map to the other by placing towers along their way. There are over a dozen different buildings with upgrades, tech research, and a whole lot of maps! There's also a built-in editor so you can make your own maps and share them with others.

Sqdef won 1st place at the GBAX 2007 Coding Competition and is a GP2X Wiz built-in game.

name: Animatch
description: One of the games that came pre-installed on the GP2X Wiz portable console.

name: IQ Jump
description:
A collection of 5 brain training style games which came pre-installed in the console GP2X Wiz. The games include:
Look for the same pictures
Look for the missing number
Addition and Subtraction
Look for the coin in the saving pocket
Crisis Ladder

name: Very Important Potato
description: A real-time steampunk strategy game were you are a potat. Potat destruction 4 styles, Plant, Mental, Energy, Insect. Gather resources, improve, defend your lab, use inventions like random gravity check, whos frying now. Place inventions in the town, for potat mayhem!

name: Propis
description: A game for the GamePark GP32.

name: Pinball Dreams
description: A port by Logik State to the GP32 (GamePark 32) handheld game console.

name: Star Dynasties Bloodlines
description: Survive and endure. Never before has the goal of Star Dynasties been more clear than within the new DLC, Bloodlines. Explore the enriched and expanded gameplay with family-driven events, features, and bonuses. Develop your dynasty as you see fit and secure a legacy to outlast generations.

name: Shooter Dual Pack I Necromunda: Hired Gun + Space Hulk: Deathwing - Enhanced Edition
description:
The Shooter Dual Pack includes:
- Necromunda: Hired Gun
- Space Hulk: Deathwing - Enhanced Edition at a reduced price.

name: Sonic the Hedgehog Extreme
description: Sonic Extreme was a prototype video game created by Vision Scape Interactive in May 2003. Proposed as a spin-off to Sega's Sonic the Hedgehog series, Sonic Extreme featured Sonic and Shadow riding hoverboards in a Green Hill Zone-themed open world, with gameplay likened to Tony Hawk's Pro Skater. It featured three gameplay modes, which included searching for keys and Chaos Emeralds and fighting or racing another player.

name: Station Overseer
description: A fantasy space station simulator with a storytelling emphasis, where the player is tasked with building a home among the stars. Witness the success and tragedy of the humans and aliens alike as the player helps them survive the cold harsh environment of outer space.

name: FruitFall Crush
description: FruitFall Crush, a true puzzle game, ideally suited to the Nintendo Switch gaming philosophy.

name: Monster Hunter Stories: Tabidachi no Shou
Mobile Suit Gundam: Iron-Blooded Orphans G
Myth: Gods of Asgard
description: Enter the Norse world and become the Norse Gods' incarnation! Experience the ultimate aestheticization of violence in battles.

name: Jianghu Simulator
description: This is a framework for a Wuxia World Simulator. The official scenario is also a comprehensive demonstration of the MOD development capabilities - players can write their own Jianghu stories in ‘Turn of Destiny’ and ‘Sandbox Mode’.

name: Siege: Apocalypse
description: Clash with your opponents in head-to-head duels in this Military PvP Card game against real players from all over the world in realistic battles. Make strategic decisions, lead military operations, build powerful decks with unique cards, and withstand the tough competition to top the seasonal leaderboards.

name: Paperly: Paper Plane Adventure
description: Go on an exciting paper plane flight adventure, learn different flight mechanics & explore different worlds. it's all about flying a paper plane, learning from previous mistakes, and heading toward a better flight in this physics-driven gameplay.

name: Game of Legends: Rise of Champions
Soul Land: Advent of the Gods
Dungeon of Despair
description: Navigate a chilling dungeon of psychological torment in this retro 2D horror game. Try to escape. You are not alone. The faster you run, the faster the relentless enemy catches up. Your heart is pounding, and it's closer with every heartbeat. The end is near...

name: Guitar Girl Match 3
description:
I wish you could be happy today with my music.
Calm and relaxing game with the Guitar Girl's performance! Be more zen!
Gather the scattered puzzles, and give the girl's daily life a special and wonderful makeover.

name: Uncle and Cat Super: Miracle Puzzle
Rugby Nations 22
description:
Fight every ruck, power through every scrum and convert every precious point. With Rugby Nations 22… Every day is a Rugby day. Let’s play!
Featuring a slew of new gameplay features, graphical improvements and huge changes to player training/progression - allowing for deeper than ever customisation of your Rugby squad.
And, for the first time, the Women’s game is fully represented on an equal footing to the men’s game.
A complete visual overhaul has seen all of the players and stadiums lovingly recreated to make this an awesome looking Rugby game.
And, of course, the gameplay has been further enhanced to offer a fresh and distinctive challenge to Rugby fans all around the World.

name: The Age of Navigation
description: It is a single-player game with the theme of navigation. Our goal is to do our best to restore the magnificent era of navigation.

name: Paradigm: Reboot
description:
Paradigm: Reboot presents a rhythm game in 3-dimensional space,
Combining MUG with elements of storytelling.

name: Honor of Heirs
description:
Assemble the mightiest medieval Order and dominate the land of Avalon!
Embark on an adventure to create the most epic hero tale!

name: Heroes Unleashed
description: The Black Stone was destroyed and evil beings began to invade the kingdom. Ned’s party was entangled in “that” incident and they were wanted. However, by current situation of kingdom, they got freedom of their movement. Collapse of kingdom by the evil invasion. The new rising of hostile tribes expelled by kingdom. The independence of Leda and conflict of it. Now, Ned is swept away by hard time. Please be there with him to overcome adversity.

name: Paradise Lost
description:
A journey felt sweet like a dream. However, a storm suddenly blew up…. The reeling ship eventually swept away by the waves and overturned. The main character, who had been drifted, opens her eyes and sees the clear blue sky of an island that does not exist on the map…. and the six unfamiliar faces that calling her name and approaching!

“E..Excuse me. Can we just talk for a minute?!”

name: Dragon Nest 2
description:
Great adventurers! You have heard the whispering call of the goddess Altea, please come back and continue to write your faith and mission together!
The continent of Altea is about to collapse, and she is waiting for your return!
The goddess Altea, the creator of Dragon Valley, was poisoned by her evil sister Vestinel and fell into a deep sleep. In her sleep, the world of Archerin was born. The invading shadows devastated this continent and destroyed life in this land. Mankind became selfish and greedy and an unprecedented calamity has befallen this pure land. Until a group of adventurers came to this land, fought against the dragon, and found the power stone that helped them awaken the sleeping goddess from her slumber and save her world.
Do you remember what happened 13 years ago? Now, the Dragon Valley Continent has been attacked by giant dragons once and the land of happiness is the brink of collapse. Do you hear the goddess' voice calling out to you in your dreams? Adventurers, please come back! Come back and save this world from darkness.
Altea is waiting for you and your friends to go home and save this world and its youth from being destroyed by these vile creatures.
All four classes will provide players with plenty of options when it comes to finding the best approach. Dungeons can be tackled solo or in groups of four or eight players while World Bosses will require coordinated efforts from all players to bring down for precious rewards.

name: Tic Tac Toe: The Ultimate Board Game
Afterschool! Survival Club
description: Afterschool! Survival Club is a simple rogue-like zombie survival game, players fight zombies by tapping at them.

name: Handball Pelota
description: Discover the famous hand ball pelota game. If you know pelota, you'll enjoy a realistic still very playable simulation of this sport.

name: Endzone: A World Apart - Distant Places
description: Being the pioneers they are, they want to reach out to other survivors and discover new and exciting places beyond the borders of the settlement. They want to uncover the Distant Places, far, far away that so many legends speak of.

name: City of Gangsters: Criminal Record
description: Take control of your outfit and engage in daring new schemes in City of Gangsters: Criminal Record.

name: What Lies in the Multiverse: Deluxe Edition
A Musical Story: Digital Deluxe Edition
description: A Musical Story Digital Deluxe Edition includes: A Musical Story Full Game, Official Soundtrack and exclusive Artbook and Wallpapers not available outside of the Deluxe Edition.

name: Dead Fury
description: Descend into hell in Dead Fury! - A fast-paced action-adventure title set amongst the rugged mountains of a post-apocalyptic New Zealand, a native blossom is the last hope for humanity after a virus brought back from Mars triggered a zombie apocalypse.

name: Zorya: The Celestial Sisters - Stellar Edition
description: In this award-winning cooperative puzzle game, play along with a friend as either Aysu or Solveig and help reunite the sister goddesses. Includes Full Game + Digital Soundtrack (.mp3 and .flac) + Digital copy of The Art of Zorya: The Celestial Sisters.

name: Sugar Crime
description: All candies have disappeared in the US because of a Sweets Prohibition. Fortunately, two clever and determined heroes Zack and Lou do not agree! They find candies and distribute them to grateful children everywhere while trying to figure out who is behind this dreadful law. Help Zack and Lou with their investigation before the police can stop them!

name: Grandma
description: This is a grandma Jumpscare horror game.

name: Your Financial Story
description: A No-Nonsense Finance Game about Personal Finance, Money Management, & Budgeting

name: Again
description: This is done by one Russian developer, the game will be constantly changing in the future, it will have an open world, a store where players will be able to buy many things for game currency, from items that restore health to armor.

name: Escape the Darkness
description: Escape the darkness is a first person horror game involving a person trying to escape a maze. The game occurs in an hospital with repetitive rooms and involve a character who caries a flashlight that tries to escape by burning the enemy.

name: Azerion
description: First / third person multiplayer shooter with single and multiplayer AI bots and monster, premade and procedural environments.

name: Night Light
description: The personifications of Night and Light learn to get along. Discover each other’s unique skills to help both Night and Light come to realize that new paths will open up if they work together.

name: Déjà Vu
description: Déjà Vu is a sci-fi puzzle platformer. The player solves puzzles through the use of clones created from actions they recorded.

name: Train Simulator: Salzburg - Rosenheim Route
description: All aboard for Austria! Take charge of cross-border passenger & freight traffic with RSSLO’s Salzburg - Rosenheim route for Train Simulator.

name: Dance Hall Brawl
description: Play as Veta, a gal trying to solve things peacefully in a dangerous world. Work to win the hearts of those in each city, taking a lot of hits without dishing any out! DANCEHALLBRAWL is a game where the most skilled players won't get hit at all!

name: Syrak: the War in the Middle-East
description: SYRAK is a card-based strategy game set during the most complex war in recent history of the Middle-East. Local or Online game have you play as the Resistance Axis or the Western Defence Organization. Use powerful Political, Espionage and Military Cards to outwit and overwhelm your opponent.

name: Monkey Mansion
description: Monkey Mansion is a high-paced online co-op horror game for 1-4 players. Your mission is to obtain the priceless relics hidden inside a lavish 1920's Russian mansion. Recover them all without getting caught by the old pet proboscis monkey that was affected by the maniacal rituals performed there.

name: Legendary Sword
description: This is the first person medieval RPG game, where you can experience the open world. Become a farmer, breed livestock, go out hunting in the sun, sneak into the castle at night as a thief, or bring your best weapons and armor to resist the invasion of the enemy. Finally, take the booty home.

name: Swords and Their Boy
description: Swords and Their Boy is a 2.5D sci-fi souls-like action about two AI swords using a mortally wounded boy to finish their task - cleanse an alien planet before its colonization.

name: Imha
description: IMHA is an action horror FPS set on a mysterious island ravaged by a demon invasion.

name: Liu Yi's strange world adventure
description: An adventure decryption type of game It mainly triggers the decryption level through the plot mode. In order to save the mainland, you embark on an unknown adventure, look for the mysterious badge of light, and get the power of the great magician!

name: Tank Hangar Simulator
description: Tank Hangar Simulator, In Your Own Hangar You Can Both Repair Tanks and Build Your Own Tank and Join the War!

name: Sky Jump
description: A journey to find something hidden in the sky on a small light aircraft. Wear VR and stand in place and enjoy adventures. There's no radical movement, and I try to play while savoring what I see.

name: Cast
description: Applauding, the cast is ready. Lighting, the shadow is sneaky. Tabing, the final is blurry. Ending, the future is dizzy.

name: Holdfast: Frontlines WW1
description: Holdfast: Frontlines is an online multiplayer first and third-person shooter set during WW1. Engage in large-scale and destructive battles of The Great War with over 150 players per server, featuring rifles, machine guns, artillery, grenades, and other iconic weaponry and mechanics from the time.

name: Might of the Stones
description: The world is in danger. An evil entity is trying to destroy the world. It is your job to stop this evil being! Do you have what is takes to save the planet?

name: MASD
description: MASD is a unique shooter/survival project. Once you have landed on the island, many challenges await you. Craft equipment, build your shelter and destroy your competitors. The availability of resources is strictly limited!

name: KeyWe: The 100th Grand Ol' Telepost Tournament
description: Postal pros Jeff and Debra have proven themselves indispensable members of the Telepost workforce, and now they’re looking to ascend to the rank of Postmasters! But first, they must conquer the annual Telepost Tournament! Do you have what it takes to tackle this Bungalow Basin tradition?

name: D.O.A
description: DOA is a 3person Shooter with Multiplayer Modes ..

name: Real Tennis
description: You can freely enjoy tennis anywhere through VR. Get trophies based on the Winning Points you get for every win. Practice swing at the training ground, compete with bots, and raise your ranking score with pvp competitions with friends!

name: Hollowsk 1999 3D
description: This town is full of familiar people whose faces cannot be remembered. Full of familiar streets and yards that never end. But you look like you’ve been here before - you do look familiar. Join the howling monoliths drowning in the haze, uncover their mysteries in a slow-burn retro horror adventure.

name: DuckHunt: Missouri Kidz
description: Don't get fooled by the simple looks of this game! The way it is played is something unseen so far in the gaming world! Using a novel patented technology you and your friends will use your cellphones to aim at the screen and shoot! Show your friends who is a real gunslinger!

name: Cube
description: Cube is a puzzle/platform minimalistic game with a rotation mechanic, your logical thinking, dexterity and precision will be challenged, try to get the best score while pass through 49 levels with progressive dificulty. It can be harder than it looks.

name: Carrier Battles 4 Guadalcanal: Submarines & Torpedo Alley Scenario
description: Play with submarines and enjoy a new scenario.

name: Lambda end Theory
description: Lambda end Theory is a cryptic and minimalist RPG about a mysterious world and its inhabitants.

name: Countryball: Europe 1890
description: Discover the 19th and 20th centuries with countryballs!

name: EDM Storm: Match 3 VR
description: Exciting match-3 puzzle game, with electronic music for climax！

name: Boomer Slayers
description: Boomer Slayers is an old-school top-down shooter with modern low-poly graphics and badass gameplay. Join friends in local co-op to slay enemies together!

name: My Train Arrives: In ten years
description: Take a look at your favorite cities in ten years. 8 cities from the original campaign will be available in this extension. The game area increased by 65%. New passenger and cargo stations appeared in all cities.

name: Lake Facade: Director's Cut
description: Explore, Fish and discover the mysteries hidden within Lake Facade. A short narrative puzzle/adventure game with multiple endings and secrets to find.

name: Smugglers of Cygnus
description: Smugglers of Cygnus places you in command of a ship in the service of that noblest profession: Commerce. Travel the galaxy. Deliver goods. Deliver goods of questionable legality for higher rates. Fend off pirates, or perhaps become one yourself...The Galaxy is yours. Come and take it.

name: Spirits of Freedom
description: Embark on this Epic Platform-Style Adventure, Inspired by the Most Iconic Games Ever. Race with WOLFY, and Fly with FOXY on a journey to save your home with the help of the Rainbow Spirits and their friends.

name: Space Attack
description: Space Attack is a retro shooter with a 1970s feel. You can upgrade your ship according to your preference. Enemy battles show physics-based behavior. The difficulty level is set low for those who are not familiar with the game.

name: Voxquest: The Firebird
description: An open world fantasy adventure in a voxel art style! Explore a massive, continuous overworld with puzzles, upgrades, a variety of weapon aspects and six dungeons. Play with keyboard or XBOX-style controller.

name: Elon
description: After a mysterious accident you are left are stranded, floating through space on a piece of a space station. Craft supplies and Hubs to expand what is now your home. But be warned space is a dangerous places where one mistake can mean certain death. Can you defy the odds and survive in space?

name: Sight and Sound Town
description: Explore the town and Chat with palsTake on rhythm based challenges from the bizarre Clay CreaturesComplete these challenges to unlock MusicRetake challenges that you’ve beaten

name: Crystal Road: Vale of Memories
description: Embark on a mystical adventure to solve the mystery of the Crystal Road. Guided by a strange voice, you find yourself in a world that has been ravaged by an all consuming fog. Romance will bloom as you establish the land and unravel the truth. Farm, fish and build your forever home in your new life!

name: Symptom of Love
description: Plunge into this story and see what happens!

name: Building Destruction
description: Building destruction - an exciting physical game aimed at destroying buildings and various structures.

name: Shale Hill Secrets
description: In this story-focused adult visual novel by Love-Joint, you suddenly gain the power to peer into people’s hidden lives. Seduce your classmates in beautiful rendered 3D art. Unravel a conspiracy, fall in love, or use your power for yourself.

name: Fall In love 2
description: Created by "Origin team", "FALL IN LOVE2" is a very classic game of finding the differences, coupled with beautiful pictures and beautiful girls with unique characteristics, it will definitely bring you a very exciting experience!

name: Trick Shot Ping Pong
description: This game is a physics based trick shot game. Improve your trick shot skills. It's a really difficult game.

name: Qrabbles
description:
Qrabbles is a physics based sandbox game where you can build your own worlds, and play in them as a sticky creature.
The game is a building game, where you can build giant parkour maps, or create tornados with fans, giant escape rooms, but what you biild is up to your imagination.

name: Tumble
description: Tumble is a 2D indie action-platformer set in a dangerous world where humanity is forced to live underground. Fight countless enemies and bosses, uncover a deep storyline and rescue those you value most... if you can make it all the way down.

name: Alma
description: Alma is an interactive narrative that captures the tension of work-life balance for healthcare workers. Play as Alma, a caring mother and pediatric nurse, who must tend to both aspects of her life. Alma is a story of self-care and the struggle to find balance in an imbalanced life.

name: The Dark
description: Single player and online multiplayer survival game set in a post-apocalyptic open world, with an open world dungeon system.

name: Alternate Universe
description: Welcome to The Alternate Universe. An action, adventure, strategy, and a simulation game.

name: A Rat's Life: The Cat Conspiracy
description: Play as a rat in this first-person action-adventure. Overcome enemies and obstacle with your rat skills. Sneak and run away from horrifying cats. Ultimately explore and meet different rats to confirm or debunk conspiracy theories in this story-rich world.

name: Red Ops Arcade
description: Red Ops Arcade is a survival and fighting game that takes place across different worlds. The player has to fight zombies, monsters, ghosts and many other enemies, using different weapons that he will find in mystery boxes. The player must reach the highest round possible, but be careful because as higher is the level, more difficult will be to finish it.

name: Neon Horizon: Eclipse
description: Neon Horizon: Eclipse is a first-person action platformer in which you have to go on an exciting adventure across eight different islands. Each island has its own unique traps and obstacles.

name: Escape Sand Dunes
description: This is a first-person shooter game,the player is surrounded by zombies，The player is free to explore the surrounding area, dodge zombies or kill them, The player needs to survive as long as possible.

name: Unlimited World Book: Retro
description: Unlimited World Book: Retro is a single-player story game about the origin story of the character Doctor Edward Retro from Unlimited World 1.

name: The Soul Stone War 2: Web of Shadows
description: Take a closer look at the motivations and politics of the major players in Cridevar! Learn more about your companions' pasts and Manerkol's Court.

name: Epicentrum: Hunt. Stream. Invade.
description: Hunt! Stream! Invasion! Become an elite Hunter and stop the Invasion of the World Eaters. Or join their collective intelligence and devour the universe. Turn-based battles and generated battles! Be in Epicentrum!

name: Alone
description: An open world survival crafting game based more on realism. Craft, hunt, farm, build, and more to come.

name: The BuildSphere: Rise of the Anomalbots
description: The BuildSphere: Rise of the Anomalbots is a cyber-cool and retro style, sci-fi scavenger hunt and puzzle solving game with platforming and obstacle course like levels. Each progressive level will challenge you to collect assets and craft your next piece of loot in order to progress in the game.

name: Existential
description: Existential is a first-person story-driven puzzle game that offers a unique solution that will put your existence into the game world.

name: Snail Story: Love Edition
description: Snail Story: Love Edition is a dating sim that is choice-driven and with multiple good and bad endings. There will be a mystery element involved, which shadows a predominantly romantic storyline.

name: Handball Manager 2022
description: The new Handball Manager 2022 DLC gives you access to the current squad lists of the season 21/22, promotions and relegations, new player images, new sponsors and many other optimizations.

name: Xio: Survival
description: Xio Survival is an open-world sandbox experience. Survive solo or enter the multiplayer-verse that is vast in size with various biomes to explore. Craft, loot, build and trade your way to riches, however, don't get too comfortable, it can be taken from you quickly.

name: Bad Guy: Neighborhood
description: Roam a violent neighborhood as you complete various objectives to unlock a large variety of unique weapons and abilities. Encounter bosses, partake in mini-games, complete tasks to earn money or cause terror to the neighborhood people in this open world third person game.

name: NoRoY
description: A dark adventure full of tense moments that will test your skills. Your main goal is to climb to the top while avoiding difficult obstacles and disturbing creatures. NoRoY is very agile, but a single mistake can cause you to lose all your progress.

name: Locotier
description: Locotier is a fully moddable Czech train game in which you can complete missions, try out trains from different time epoch, or just ride.

name: Kickrexing
description: Kickrexing brings you the most exhilarating, no holds barred t-rex free kickboxing experience ever seen in the history of rexkind. Featuring ultra-realistic mocap from real t-rex champions with amazing graphics built to grantee that you’ll be sure to feel every kick, punch and tail swing.

name: BangBang PewPew
description: Finally, modern lightguns have become available for the PC that bring back the classic feeling of aiming down the sights. It’s time for the games to catch up! 25 lightgun challenges. Hot-seat multiplayer. Online challenges and leaderboards. Customizable targets.

name: Battle of Finland: Winter War
description: Battle of Finland: Winter War is a 2D side-scrolling action platformer. The Soviet Union began the conquest of Finland on November 30 1939, thus the Winter War was started. Can you help small Finland stop the red army steam rolling over Finland?

name: Jack Saves Easter
description: Jack Saves Easter is a family friendly game where you play as Jack the Rabbit. Use your skills and wits to help Jack recover various Essence Shards that will restore The Ancient Tree Eggdrasyl. Solve puzzles and clues that will help you save Easter for All !

name: Story of You: The Allied Kingdoms
description: Story of You: The Allied Kingdoms is a game about choices and consequences. See your character change according to the ways of life you choose, through a journey of discovery.

name: Never out of Time
description: Survive in an ocean of bullets by dodging, shooting at your foes and manipulating time. You can take as much time as you need and even "do over": You set the tempo of the action. Will you be able to conquer the space station?

name: Moto Mouse Stunt Mania
description: Moto Mouse Mania is a fun adventure and action racing game with cute little mouse with different bikes and nice animation. Not all Mice should be hated and after all this one is a cute and loveable.

name: Number Wars
description: You will not believe doing math can be so fun. Looking for some fun and thrill while doing math?

name: Cute Snake
description: Help the cute snake to cross the maze. Relax and enjoy this cute and minimalist experience.

name: Loading Zone
description: The Loading zone is a puzzle game, in which you will by tasked to load up different cars with boxes of different shapes and sizes.

name: Ball Pain
description: Ball Pain is next in line to join the ranks of Rage Games. Can you get to the top before you start raging?

name: Scorpion Overdrive
description: Scorpion Overdrive is a fast paced, third person shooter, combined with tower defense style turrets and weapon placements. Enemies spawn in furious hordes as you gun them down and strategically place turrets and traps to help cover you and your equipment.

name: Push the Sheep
description: A puzzle game where you have to push the sheep to make each one graze.

name: Aracnidium
description: Earth has been invaded by android spiders. Bob's family is in danger. Spiders are getting into houses from all sides. Find the right angle and shoot the spiders. Help Bob in this mission.

name: Radiometric Dating
description: A visual novel/dating simulator where you can date rocks! You play as a geology student who gets transported to a magical world during field camp. Meet handsome princes and navigate through magic encounters to find a way home!

name: Master Chess Ultimate
description:
Play your favorite chess game in a classical setting of Master Chess!

Play with a friend or against computer's artificial intelligence, choosing from three difficulty levels.

name: Smashball
description: Smashball is a SciFi Sports game with some minor RPG features to add immersion. Take on the challenge to become one of the planets leading athletes, celebrated by thousands of hysterical fans. Soar through the air, dodging opponents in order to score goals and bring glory to your fanbase.

name: Inertia
description: You're stranded in space in an asteroid field. Use your ship to smash through fuel-rich asteroids for points and fuel, and use any power-ups you find along the way. But remember, an empty fuel tank is just as deadly as an asteroid. The void of space is a tough place to be, but you can't stop now.

name: GoKart: New Mexico
description: Start your engines and prepare for the ultimate driving experience. Compete against the clock or up to 3 of your friends, choosing from a diverse set of stunning and challenging tracks.

name: Brothers
description: Take care of your family! A family is under threat from a group of people, help them find a safe place, go through chases, create ways to escape the danger, and see the end of this story.

name: Ortharion: The Last Battle
description: The Mage Ortharion has chosen you for The Last Battle! Make the right choices as you explore a world filled with magic and secrets. Improve your character in multiple ways and manage an adventurer's guild.

name: Grand Theft Rome
description: Lead roman, greek, chinese, egyptian, or knights into battle against other factions. Win by giving specific commands like box, circle lined formations and fighting alongside your troops in this ancient battle simulator.

name: Pusher
description: Pusher is a box-world or sokoban type game. Fight your way through a mixture of 50 levels, ever increasing in difficulty. The goal of the game is to push boxes around until they are all in the designated positions, but this is easier said than done.

name: Bassmaster Fishing 2022: Lake Hartwell
description: Get ready to take on the monster Lake Hartwell and the most professional bass fishing tournament – The Bassmaster Classic. It’s time to go head-to-head with the competition and compete in a 3-round final on the Bassmaster 2022 Classic venue to become the champion and take home the coveted trophy.

name: Red Solstice 2: Survivors - Condatis Group
description: Experience a new story line with new and old characters and settings. Take on the role as Marshal and survive by any means.
